or computing hash: %w\", err)\n52\t\t}\n53\t\treturn hasher.Sum(nil), nil\n54\t}\n55\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_vrtx_01StZ8bivggpJ9wizKSD3pYH","session_id":"d92bfeb3-c200-4c47-98a5-9b3219bcc18c","uuid":"64ad85e7-f91e-4303-85d8-21f3b0cbdafc","timestamp":"2026-06-22T20:58:10.422Z","subagent_type":"Explore","task_description":"Find MachineConfig merge/render ordering logic"}
